data.description:
PHOTOS WILL BE UP FRIDAY MORNING! 
 Beautifully remodeled Lockmar Estates home on an oversized .34 acre lot, with many upgrades including a 2023 Roof, 2023 Double Pane Energy Efficient windows, 2022 A/C, 2022 Hot Water Heater, 2021 Hurricane Rated Garage Bay Door, 2021 Hurricane Shutters (3 Rolldown, the rest are manual aluminum), 2021 All New Duct Work, 2021 Chimney Cap.  New Carpet in Primary Bedroom 2024!  Closets have reconfigurable shelving.  Double gate to back yard to park your boat!  Enjoy the evenings and weekends on your screened patio!  Short drive to elementary school, beach, shopping and restaurants.  Easy access to I-95!
